	<Description>Higher Karma Requirements

	Increases the Karma requirements to gain Karma levels.

	Changes made by this mod:
	[list]
	[*] The requirements to increase the Karma levels have been increased.
	[*] The amount of increase depends upon the option selected while installing the mod.
	[/list]

	Available Options:
	[list]
	[*] [b]More Karma[/b]: Karma requirements for each level are multiplied by 2.
	[*] [b]Still More Karma[/b]: Karma requirements for each level are multiplied by 3.
	[*] [b]Much More Karma[/b]: Karma requirements for each level are multiplied by 5.
	[*] [b]Lots More Karma[/b]: Karma requirements for each level are multiplied by 7.
	[*] [b]God-like Karma[/b]: Karma requirements for each level are multiplied by 10.
	[/list]

	Other Information:
	[list]
	[*] It is recommended to start a new game when installing this mod (or uninstalling it).
	[*] This mod can be installed on an existing save game if the player has not gained [i]any[/i] Karma levels, i.e. they are at Karma level 0. They can have Karma points, but not Karma levels.
	[*] Once this mod is installed, it is [b]NOT[/b] recommended to uninstall it, or to change the selected Karma multiplier option for that particular save game. Doing so may cause problems to occur in your save.
	[*] This mod appears to be co-op friendly. However, further testing may be necessary to confirm this. If you obtain any evidence supporting or disproving this hypothesis, feel free to contact me on Nexus Mods(link below)/Discord. I go by the same name on both those platforms.
	[/list]

	Credits:
	[list]
	[*] [size=1][color=lightgreen]Author: [/color][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/users/32262030][b]LinkHero95[/b][/url][/size]
	[/list]
	</Description>

